caption:
Nothing says epic Game Day feast like the legendary All Madden Turducken 🦃🐥🐓 from @gourmetbutcherblock.

This Louisiana creation—three birds, two types of stuffing—became iconic when John Madden couldn’t stop talking about it on live TV in ‘96. For over three decades, this family-run butcher shop has been shipping Turduckens across the country, keeping football fans well-fed and obsessed. 

Serve it alongside pralines, beignets, and King Cake to turn your New Orleans  tailgate from ordinary to MVP status. #turducken #gamedayfood #tailgateparty #nolaeats
